The company representative is called...

117
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:37,000
Xiao Yang.

118
00:09:37,870 --> 00:09:39,320
Xiao Yang?

119
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:42,080
Oh no! Send me the address.

120
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:43,820
Let me go.

121
00:09:44,980 --> 00:09:46,890
Let me go!

122
00:09:50,930 --> 00:09:54,390
You can drink the wine you didn't finish last time.

123
00:09:54,390 --> 00:09:56,480
If you make me happy today,

124
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:59,610
who knows? Maybe I'll go easy on you.

125
00:09:59,610 --> 00:10:01,240
Xiao Yang,

126
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:06,670
if you hurt me today, watch out. Fu Yancheng will make you wish you were dead.

127
00:10:09,030 --> 00:10:11,440
Would I be afraid of him?

128
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:12,960
Fu Yancheng is so heartless.

129
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:15,480
He destroyed my family.

